title: Super Wild Card Weekend Bets
description:
Warren Sharp and Joe House break down every game from the super wild card weekend, and Joe House begins his journey to go 13-0 in playoff bets this year.

Bills - Colts (14:50)
Rams - Seahawks (31:55)
Washington Football Team - Buccaneers (45:35)
Ravens - Titans (1:02:04)
Bears - Saints (1:14:35)
Browns - Steelers (1:22:35)

Hosts: Warren Sharp and Joe House
